text: Kiischpelt is a commune in Luxembourg. It is part of the canton of Wiltz. The administrative center is Wilwerwiltz. Kiischpelt was created on 1 January 2006 from the former communes of Kautenbach and Wilwerwiltz. As of 2019, 1,201 people live here.
